headline.main: Actress Emma Watson Says Revealing Photo Does Not Undermine Feminism
headline.print_headline: Actress Emma Watson Says Revealing Photo Does Not Undermine Feminism

lead_paragraph: British actress Emma Watson hit back at critics who said she betrayed her feminist ideals by posing for a revealing picture in Vanity Fair magazine where parts of her breasts were exposed.
